  "description": "A close-up photograph features a vibrant purple tulip in full bloom. The flower is positioned slightly off-center, facing towards the left. The interior of the tulip reveals a complex structure: dark brown stamens with yellow tips surrounding a central green pistil. The petals exhibit a gradient of purple hues, transitioning from deeper shades at the edges to lighter tones near the center. A bright white line runs along one petal, creating a highlight. Behind the tulip, blurry green foliage and a warm-toned wooden background are visible. The lighting is soft and diffused, emphasizing the delicate details of the flower.",
